<br />\n但只係十二年嘅事，<br />\n到咗真正廿年之後，<br />\n月薪真係不敢想像！"},{"pid":"aed7d60f4583708d6ebcae4320b06f97240c1d9a","tid":2492550,"uid":336583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9060305817124c4962eba00896d5347d17a79255","tid":2492550,"uid":217993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T15:27:03.000Z","msg":"呢家呢份有冇錢途先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T15:54:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b32597856756f10d56d1b877e54d665a9db4b7ea","tid":2492550,"uid":84176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T15:56:31.000Z","msg":"29K 冗員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8827a9b7a3c37d7ceb503615556ef50c006d454","tid":2492550,"uid":60635,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"01e1e02807f409067c7558370284cea33877241f","tid":2492550,"uid":238214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T15:28:50.000Z","msg":"Local大公司5日 唔洗諗<br />\n美資係高薪D 不過一縮皮 就會成team team killed<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T16:05:15.000Z","msg":"美資炒人唔手軟，成個分公司收皮都係比半個月通知<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c90c0f9706c7c5ee0dc849a2ec99f590b8a5d4b0","tid":2492550,"uid":184103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22af19a371362458111f5593ab85c493f66dddcc","tid":2492550,"uid":336583,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"quote":{"pid":"e3528fbb8ee60831de01a799d6890ed6efa9bace","tid":2492550,"uid":74816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T14:33:38.000Z","msg":"想知宜家份工咩行頭？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T15:03:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T16:18:24.000Z","msg":"知你做咩位先答到你<br />\n不